cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

The paper deals with object detection, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The focus is on underwater object detection, which involves robotics and automation (cs.RO). The paper proposes an augmentation method that characterizes interactions among images, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method aims to improve the generalization of object detectors, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with object detection in a specific environment, which involves graphics (cs.GR).
